-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Nature of the fork / summary of changes
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

- Cross-platform rewrite (macOS / Windows / Linux) on a Rust core
  (Tauri 2 + React), replacing the macOS-only Swift / AVFoundation implementation.
- Media engine built on FFmpeg (decode/encode) + wgpu (compositing) + cpal (audio),
  replacing AVFoundation's declarative composition.
- Self-hosted / BYOK generative-AI backend. The upstream generative-AI processing
  is closed-source and is NOT part of this fork; OpenTake provides its own.
